{"tid":1656453,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"專業清算師召喚手足各自出信 迫令屋宇署嚴正執法","createTime":"2019-10-15T15:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T05:10:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"37f4463adb208715ce1f170ab93f1be8dcd8ecec","tid":1656453,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:01:49.000Z","msg":"【Buddy仔流藍血就有特權？不了！召喚網民十月圍Buddy仔、誓要拆佢生招牌】<br />\n<br />\n平時屋宇署天台屋就照拆，趕人瞓街就嚴正執法。TVBuddy 就有特權？全城追擊老僭Buddy！再次召喚所有網民幫手，齊齊透過1823 舉報，向屋宇署施壓，專業清算師期望動員1000位手足各自出信，迫令屋宇署嚴正執法。<br />\n<br />\n1、用1823 app作以下舉報 或<br />\n2、直接Email到<br />\ntellme@1823.gov.hk; devbenq@devb.gov.hk; enquiry@bd.gov.hk<br />\n=================<br />\n<br />\n敬啟者：<br />\n<br />\n要求屋宇署嚴正執法即時安排承辦商清拆TVBuddy大型戶外僭建物事宜<br />\n<br />\n鑑於有報道指將軍澳電視城TVBuddy 僭建物已向屋宇署提出補救方案加建鐵架穩固，並獲批准保留僭建物而無須遵守「先清拆、後入則」的規定，請問消息是否屬實？<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%E2%80%A6&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=48f19e35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%E2%80%A6&h=9f1da924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php&hellip;</a><br />\n<br />\n一、<br />\n若是，請問TVB 是何時提交申請？屋宇署又於何時批准申請？ 特事特辦，效率其高，有官商勾結之嫌。本人於10月3日入信質詢Buddy屬優先取締項目一事仍未回覆，便急急拍板定案保留，惹人懷疑。<br />\n<br />\n二、<br />\n若是，批准採取「補救方案」的準則為何，包括該等準則適用於哪些類型的僭建物；屋宇署有否公布該等準則的詳情；如沒有公布，原因為何；若不是適用於所有人，原因為何；<br />\n<br />\n關於二之準則問題，2012年時任發展局局長陳茂波已於2012年12月5日在立法會作出回覆。在此不作長述，有興趣請參看：<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/&hellip;/gener&hellip;/201212/05/P201212050399.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2F%E2%80%A6%2Fgener%E2%80%A6%2F201212%2F05%2FP201212050399.htm&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=992bbdc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/&hellip;/gener&hellip;/201212/05/P201212050399.htm</a><br />\n<br />\nTvbuddy首見於2007年1月29日無綫電視的宣傳片，顯然不是與將軍澳電視城一同落成。根據前局長回覆，屋宇署需要即時就TVBuddy 採取取締行動。<br />\n<br />\n三、<br />\n由新聞圖片可見，工人為了維修/清潔僭建Buddy，工人在沒有保護措施下高空工作及危站天台邊沿，險象環生，違反高空工作指引及職安健要求。我們要求勞工署介入事件調查及檢控。<br />\n<br />\n屋宇署更應早日發出清拆令以正視聽，如有意外發生，屋宇署署長甚至發展局局長是否願意向公眾及傳媒致歉及問責下台？<br />\n<br />\n市民 陳先生上<br />\n<br />\n=================<br />\n<br />\n@photo credited to 蘋果日報<br />\n<br />\n#專業清算師<br />\nFB：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/revengehi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frevengehi%2F&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=66c56936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/revengehi/</a><br />\nTG：<a href=\"https://t.me/revengehi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevengehi&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=8703c08d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revengehi</a><br />\n<br />\n#專業清算師 #齊心齊上齊落 #党媒 #事實與真相 #違法僭建物 #五大訴求缺一不可 #拆你生招牌 #buddy仔安心上路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/73152472_139315637442548_5834445125786271744_n.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_oc=AQmFSOlxaf8-l9e1XdCLJXRNmT7v4K1VTplrb9WuLJhL7hNbmANtj17p2rxO1dOKuDk&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=f077ff5ca180ff7e9173f7330ccdbcf7&amp;oe=5E324E12\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F73152472_139315637442548_5834445125786271744_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_oc%3DAQmFSOlxaf8-l9e1XdCLJXRNmT7v4K1VTplrb9WuLJhL7hNbmANtj17p2rxO1dOKuDk%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Df077ff5ca180ff7e9173f7330ccdbcf7%26oe%3D5E324E12&h=268d8723&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d84ba673935011dcf607ea763faeb01e55041c8","tid":1656453,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afoWPNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafoWPNY.jpg&h=041452ea&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid"